      "title": "About Me",
      "description": "I am an intermediate Python developer transitioning into the worlds of Data Science and Data Engineering . My journey began with mastering the fundamentals of Pythonbuilding everything from expense trackers to chatbotsand has evolved into a passion for architecting data solutions. Currently, I am expanding my expertise in web development and AI automation through my agency, FlyVark AI, while preparing for an MSc in Data Science. I thrive at the intersection of clean code and actionable data.",
